Jenkins Pipeline Execution:

Jenkins pipeline automates the deployment process, including code checkout, dependency installation, and deployment to SAP BTP.
Node.js Application on SAP BTP:

The application, running on SAP BTP, serves HTTP requests and generates telemetry data using OpenTelemetry.
OpenTelemetry Prometheus Exporter:

OpenTelemetry captures metrics and exposes them at the /metrics endpoint in Prometheus format.
Prometheus Scraping:

Prometheus server scrapes the /metrics endpoint periodically to collect telemetry data from the application
